WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.830
Welcome and good evening, family.

00:00:03.840 --> 00:00:06.150
Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:07.909
I'm going to go over some of the things

00:00:07.919 --> 00:00:09.830
that the Lord showed us in our last

00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:12.390
prayer video, and I'll go over some

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:14.070
things that are new today that I've

00:00:14.080 --> 00:00:16.870
gotten over the last 24 hours praying

00:00:16.880 --> 00:00:20.550
with the Lord.

00:00:23.439 --> 00:00:26.630
Holy Spirit, I invite

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:30.310
you in this time of prayer. I thank

00:00:30.320 --> 00:00:32.310
you, Lord, that it is uninterrupted and unhindered

00:00:32.320 --> 00:00:35.110
by any satanic or demonic force. Father,

00:00:35.120 --> 00:00:37.430
I ask you to pray

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:39.430
through me. Holy Spirit, I ask

00:00:39.440 --> 00:00:40.869
you to speak through my vocal cords and

00:00:40.879 --> 00:00:43.270
think through my mind. None of me and

00:00:43.280 --> 00:00:46.869
all of you, in Jesus'name. Amen.

00:00:46.879 --> 00:00:50.229
Holy Spirit, we invite Him and we're so

00:00:50.239 --> 00:00:52.790
thankful for Him.

00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:55.270
I think the last prayer video was

00:00:55.280 --> 00:00:56.950
probably one of my favorites of the year

00:00:56.960 --> 00:00:59.670
so far. I don't know how many people

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:03.430
watched that, but it truly blessed me.

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:06.870
Everything the Lord showed me about

00:01:06.880 --> 00:01:09.429
the revival with John Kilpatrick and

00:01:09.439 --> 00:01:11.670
the churches around America with Perry

00:01:11.670 --> 00:01:11.680
Stone—I've

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:14.710
just been

00:01:14.720 --> 00:01:16.550
meditating on it, soaking it

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:20.390
in. We can go from one

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:22.789
place to another and just

00:01:22.799 --> 00:01:25.030
take for granted what God has done

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:26.710
through this channel and what He's

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:29.990
showing us so gracefully.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:32.390
Or you can take the moment to pause

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:35.190
and just really

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:38.310
breathe in that fragrance of who He is

00:01:38.320 --> 00:01:41.350
and what He's about to do in this earth.

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:44.310
It's amazing. I

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:45.590
don't want to take for granted those

00:01:45.600 --> 00:01:49.109
times; they're precious to me. Diana and

00:01:49.109 --> 00:01:49.119
I have

00:01:49.119 --> 00:01:51.350
been

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:53.830
meditating,

00:01:55.439 --> 00:01:56.789
running those things through our

00:01:56.789 --> 00:01:56.799
minds and

00:01:56.799 --> 00:01:58.870
thinking about what God

00:01:58.880 --> 00:02:01.670
said about Pastor John Kilpatrick. I

00:02:01.680 --> 00:02:03.749
don't even know them

00:02:03.749 --> 00:02:03.759
or

00:02:03.759 --> 00:02:06.709
their church, but I've watched some of the

00:02:06.719 --> 00:02:08.949
online services

00:02:08.949 --> 00:02:08.959
to

00:02:08.959 --> 00:02:11.110
catch up with some of the things

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:13.910
he's saying. They're

00:02:13.910 --> 00:02:13.920
a

00:02:13.920 --> 00:02:16.390
hungry church. He had a

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:19.110
sermon series

00:02:19.110 --> 00:02:19.120
in

00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:21.430
his archives; I

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:23.910
listened to two of them and they really

00:02:23.920 --> 00:02:25.430
blessed me. I was trying to think

00:02:25.430 --> 00:02:25.440
of

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:26.869
what it was called,

00:02:26.879 --> 00:02:29.830
but

00:02:29.840 --> 00:02:31.910
it was phenomenal.

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:33.830
He preaches amazingly.

00:02:33.830 --> 00:02:33.840
I encourage

00:02:33.840 --> 00:02:35.830
you all

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:37.910
to listen to it.

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:46.869
We've listened to a

00:02:46.879 --> 00:02:48.070
bunch of them now

00:02:48.080 --> 00:02:49.589
because I

00:02:49.599 --> 00:02:52.150
wanted to know if we're right.

00:02:52.160 --> 00:02:53.670
Whenever you're hearing in the

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:55.910
spirit

00:02:55.920 --> 00:02:57.430
and the Lord's showing you things,

00:02:57.440 --> 00:02:59.589
you don't want to be flaky.

00:02:59.599 --> 00:03:02.149
I don't

00:03:02.159 --> 00:03:04.229
want to be a part of the flakiness; I

00:03:04.239 --> 00:03:05.589
want to flow with the Holy Spirit.

00:03:05.599 --> 00:03:07.990
If it's off, it's off. I'm not here to

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:10.229
make excuses. If I miss it, I

00:03:10.239 --> 00:03:12.229
miss it, but I want to be quick to tell

00:03:12.239 --> 00:03:14.949
you.

00:03:14.959 --> 00:03:16.630
The Lord is telling me

00:03:16.640 --> 00:03:19.750
that He's going to renew his veins and

00:03:19.760 --> 00:03:22.309
his arteries,

00:03:22.319 --> 00:03:25.190
renewing

00:03:25.200 --> 00:03:27.670
his body like the

00:03:27.680 --> 00:03:29.270
eagles. The

00:03:29.280 --> 00:03:31.270
glory of the Lord is coming on John

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:34.550
Kilpatrick like Moses. I saw him

00:03:34.560 --> 00:03:37.430
sitting in a chair on his platform,

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:39.030
and

00:03:39.040 --> 00:03:41.990
the glory of the Lord was

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:44.470
tangible in the atmosphere of the

00:03:44.480 --> 00:03:46.309
church.

00:03:46.319 --> 00:03:48.229
He was like a big papa bear

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:55.589
watching over the flock as the shepherd

00:03:55.599 --> 00:03:58.070
of that church. The glory of the

00:03:58.080 --> 00:04:01.270
Lord was tangible.

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:03.270
Do you remember I told you mist would

00:04:03.280 --> 00:04:06.229
show up in services and, as it

00:04:06.239 --> 00:04:08.630
dissipates, it would leave gold

00:04:08.640 --> 00:04:11.030
dust on people's skin?

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:13.509
That's what I saw coming

00:04:13.519 --> 00:04:18.150
even in his church—a mist of

00:04:18.160 --> 00:04:21.670
the glory where the residue of the glory

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:24.629
of the Lord would leave a type of gold

00:04:24.639 --> 00:04:27.189
dust. I know there has been mockery

00:04:27.199 --> 00:04:30.870
of this, like people trying to

00:04:30.880 --> 00:04:34.629
fake it, but the Lord said to me,

00:04:36.320 --> 00:04:37.430
'Brandon, there's

00:04:37.440 --> 00:04:40.710
going to be an authentic move of this

00:04:40.720 --> 00:04:44.150
that

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:46.710
won't be mocked, fake,

00:04:46.710 --> 00:04:46.720
or

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:48.870
man-made.'This

00:04:48.880 --> 00:04:51.270
is going to be a tangible

00:04:51.280 --> 00:04:54.390
visitation of the Lord that nobody's going to be

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:56.710
able to

00:04:56.720 --> 00:04:58.790
duplicate other than

00:04:58.800 --> 00:05:03.510
Jesus. I saw that at that church

00:05:03.520 --> 00:05:05.990
and I saw everybody getting healed. I

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.950
saw the glory of the Lord.

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:13.270
I know he's probably getting

00:05:13.280 --> 00:05:14.790
older,

00:05:14.800 --> 00:05:17.189
but the Lord said, 'I'm about to

00:05:17.199 --> 00:05:20.390
give him a second wind, a new

00:05:20.400 --> 00:05:22.390
wind of my glory, a new wind of my

00:05:22.400 --> 00:05:25.189
presence upon his

00:05:25.189 --> 00:05:25.199
church.'What

00:05:25.199 --> 00:05:26.950
happened at Pensacola and

00:05:26.950 --> 00:05:26.960
the

00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:29.270
Brownsville Revival will be times

00:05:29.270 --> 00:05:29.280
ten.

00:05:29.280 --> 00:05:31.430
I thought that was a very

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:33.029
interesting number when the Lord said

00:05:33.039 --> 00:05:36.150
that to me because

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:38.310
usually, the Lord

00:05:38.310 --> 00:05:38.320
deals in

00:05:38.320 --> 00:05:40.790
double for the trouble

00:05:40.790 --> 00:05:40.800
or

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:42.950
sevenfold

00:05:42.960 --> 00:05:45.670
or

00:05:48.390 --> 00:05:48.400
a

00:05:49.749 --> 00:05:49.759
hundredfold.

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:55.830
He said times ten. The

00:05:55.840 --> 00:05:58.629
weightiness of the Brownsville Revival

00:06:04.639 --> 00:06:06.629
would be times ten in what's about to

00:06:06.639 --> 00:06:08.550
happen at the Church of His Presence

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:12.870
there in

00:06:12.870 --> 00:06:12.880
Daphne,

00:06:12.880 --> 00:06:15.990
Alabama.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:18.550
All glory to Jesus; I'm excited

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:20.469
for that congregation. Then He

00:06:20.479 --> 00:06:23.430
showed me Perry Stone.

00:06:23.440 --> 00:06:25.110
In the vision, the

00:06:25.120 --> 00:06:28.790
Lord showed me John Kilpatrick by

00:06:28.800 --> 00:06:31.510
himself,

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:37.270
but Perry

00:06:37.280 --> 00:06:40.550
had someone standing beside him,

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:43.350
a

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:46.150
younger

00:06:46.160 --> 00:06:49.670
person

00:06:49.680 --> 00:06:51.990
helping him.

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:54.230
This would be around the clock, 24

00:06:54.230 --> 00:06:54.240
hours a

00:06:54.240 --> 00:06:56.150
day. I'm talking about

00:06:56.160 --> 00:06:58.629
glorious church services that you

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:10.390
just don't want to

00:07:10.400 --> 00:07:12.550
unhook from.

00:07:12.560 --> 00:07:14.150
Brother Hagin used to say all the

00:07:14.160 --> 00:07:15.670
time that sometimes you

00:07:15.670 --> 00:07:15.680
just have to unhook

00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:17.189
from

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:21.510
a

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:26.230
service. But

00:07:26.240 --> 00:07:30.070
what I saw coming were services

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:33.589
that you just don't unhook from until

00:07:33.589 --> 00:07:33.599
you feel

00:07:33.599 --> 00:07:37.589
it lift.

00:07:37.599 --> 00:07:40.629
God's about to show up and show

00:07:40.639 --> 00:07:42.230
off in people's lives.

00:07:42.240 --> 00:07:44.550
I

00:07:44.560 --> 00:07:47.270
saw

00:07:47.280 --> 00:07:49.830
massive silos again.

00:07:51.510 --> 00:07:51.520
When

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:55.909
I went to heaven before, the Lord

00:07:55.919 --> 00:07:58.550
allowed me to see the silos with the

00:07:58.560 --> 00:08:00.710
body

00:08:00.710 --> 00:08:00.720
parts—eyes,

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:04.150
ears, people that needed creative

00:08:04.160 --> 00:08:06.869
miracles.

00:08:12.879 --> 00:08:15.350
Those silos were full of parts, and the

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:17.670
Lord said, 'I'm emptying my silos,

00:08:17.680 --> 00:08:21.270
Brandon. There's no need for them up here

00:08:21.280 --> 00:08:23.430
for what I'm about to

00:08:23.430 --> 00:08:23.440
do.'This

00:08:23.440 --> 00:08:26.309
will be the greatest grace

00:08:26.319 --> 00:08:28.550
explosion,

00:08:28.560 --> 00:08:31.670
for

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:34.870
it's the

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:37.190
goodness of God that brings man to

00:08:37.200 --> 00:08:39.990
repentance.

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:50.550
Goodness and mercy are about to show

00:08:50.560 --> 00:08:52.389
up and show off in your life.

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:57.430
I saw waves,

00:08:57.440 --> 00:09:00.310
and these waves

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:03.590
were full of body parts—whatever you

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:09.030
needed: kidneys, hearts, lungs, a

00:09:09.040 --> 00:09:11.990
spleen, a pancreas,

00:09:11.990 --> 00:09:12.000
or

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:15.030
livers.

00:09:15.040 --> 00:09:16.550
I don't want to call them

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:19.030
body parts. A body part is not an organ.

00:09:19.040 --> 00:09:21.110
I guess a body part is like

00:09:21.120 --> 00:09:23.110
a finger, or hand, or whatever, but these

00:09:23.120 --> 00:09:24.949
were

00:09:24.949 --> 00:09:24.959
organs—like

00:09:24.959 --> 00:09:26.870
what you need to sustain life, what

00:09:26.880 --> 00:09:29.509
you have to have. They were inside of

00:09:29.519 --> 00:09:33.509
these waves. And as the wave would

00:09:33.519 --> 00:09:36.150
crash into the church, into the

00:09:36.160 --> 00:09:39.269
revival, there was another wave. You

00:09:39.279 --> 00:09:41.110
know how sometimes when

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:44.710
you see a massive wave on the beach,

00:09:44.720 --> 00:09:47.590
it takes a little bit of time for

00:09:47.600 --> 00:09:51.110
the wave to come back?

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:54.070
These waves were right upon each other.

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:56.230
That's why he started saying, 'The glory,

00:09:56.240 --> 00:09:58.949
the glory, the

00:09:58.959 --> 00:10:00.230
glory.'Every

00:10:00.240 --> 00:10:03.110
time I said 'the

00:10:03.110 --> 00:10:03.120
glory,'those

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:05.990
were waves

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:08.630
crashing in and bringing the

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:10.870
supply, bringing whatever

00:10:10.870 --> 00:10:10.880
you

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:13.269
needed. And he

00:10:13.279 --> 00:10:15.750
said, 'Receive it as a

00:10:15.750 --> 00:10:15.760
child.'Remember

00:10:15.760 --> 00:10:18.470
what he said? He said, 'It's time for you

00:10:18.480 --> 00:10:20.949
to receive it as a child. Don't come as

00:10:20.959 --> 00:10:23.590
spiritual adults. Come as little

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:25.670
children unto the Father,'because he

00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:27.990
said that's the kind of faith it

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:29.509
takes.

00:10:29.519 --> 00:10:31.110
It's like whenever you tell

00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:32.710
your little child,

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:34.150
'Honey, we're going to go to the

00:10:34.150 --> 00:10:34.160
store,'they

00:10:34.160 --> 00:10:36.230
just trust. They just believe it.

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:38.470
There's no doubt; doubt is taught. The

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:40.630
Lord said

00:10:40.640 --> 00:10:42.710
it's because of

00:10:42.710 --> 00:10:42.720
mistrust.

00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:44.470
You might disappoint them, and they

00:10:44.480 --> 00:10:48.150
have a seed of mistrust because of

00:10:48.160 --> 00:10:50.150
you not fulfilling what you said. But

00:10:50.160 --> 00:10:53.750
God is a God that doesn't come up

00:10:53.760 --> 00:10:56.949
short. His hand is always full

00:10:56.959 --> 00:10:59.269
and ready to give unto his children.

00:10:59.269 --> 00:10:59.279
The

00:10:59.279 --> 00:11:00.550
Lord said, 'Come to me as little

00:11:00.560 --> 00:11:02.550
children.'I

00:11:02.560 --> 00:11:04.470
saw

00:11:04.480 --> 00:11:07.829
the wave of God's

00:11:07.839 --> 00:11:10.949
glory and I saw great

00:11:10.959 --> 00:11:12.790
finances. And he said, 'Do you see that

00:11:12.790 --> 00:11:12.800
money?'I

00:11:12.800 --> 00:11:15.110
said, 'Yeah, I can see

00:11:15.110 --> 00:11:15.120
it.'But

00:11:15.120 --> 00:11:16.949
a lot of times when he's

00:11:16.959 --> 00:11:18.470
talking, I don't tell everything. I'm here

00:11:18.470 --> 00:11:18.480
and

00:11:18.480 --> 00:11:21.030
I'm seeing—it's all so

00:11:21.040 --> 00:11:22.790
real. Everything is what the Lord is

00:11:22.800 --> 00:11:24.870
showing me. I saw gold coins. I saw

00:11:24.880 --> 00:11:26.710
things that the Lord showed me. Brandon, this is

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:29.990
the outpouring of finances. As I

00:11:30.000 --> 00:11:31.990
prayed tonight,

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:34.150
we were seeing the glory

00:11:34.150 --> 00:11:34.160
and

00:11:34.160 --> 00:11:36.550
the tangible presence of the Lord

00:11:36.550 --> 00:11:36.560
in

00:11:36.560 --> 00:11:39.269
these services. It was for

00:11:39.279 --> 00:11:42.790
the youth; it was for the people.

00:11:42.800 --> 00:11:44.870
He said, 'I told you there has to be a

00:11:44.880 --> 00:11:48.710
foundation of wealth, a wealth

00:11:48.710 --> 00:11:48.720
transfer.'People

00:11:48.720 --> 00:11:50.470
go, 'I don't like talking

00:11:50.480 --> 00:11:51.670
about it because I'm going to talk more

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:53.430
about the blood of Jesus, I'm going to

00:11:53.440 --> 00:11:55.190
talk more about the healing power of

00:11:55.190 --> 00:11:55.200
God.'But

00:11:55.200 --> 00:11:57.509
there's a part of it because

00:11:57.519 --> 00:12:00.710
there's been such a bad taste in a

00:12:00.720 --> 00:12:02.150
lot of the body of Christ, especially in

00:12:02.160 --> 00:12:03.670
the charismatic circles, about

00:12:03.680 --> 00:12:05.430
finances because of things a lot of

00:12:05.440 --> 00:12:07.509
preachers focused on in the

00:12:07.519 --> 00:12:09.509
past. The Lord said, 'Listen, there's

00:12:09.519 --> 00:12:11.509
a new wave of glory.

00:12:11.519 --> 00:12:13.509
There's a new wave of my finances for a

00:12:13.519 --> 00:12:16.150
remnant of one percent.'Do you understand? It

00:12:16.160 --> 00:12:17.269
won't be everybody because he can't

00:12:17.279 --> 00:12:19.430
trust everybody with it. If he can't get

00:12:19.440 --> 00:12:21.590
it through you, he won't get it to you.

00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:23.110
And the Lord said to me, 'I'm

00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:24.870
going to bless those that will

00:12:24.880 --> 00:12:27.430
help with this end-time harvest.

00:12:27.440 --> 00:12:28.949
There's going to be a great outpouring

00:12:28.959 --> 00:12:31.670
for the end-time harvest,

00:12:31.670 --> 00:12:31.680
Brandon.'And

00:12:31.680 --> 00:12:32.870
that's what he was talking to me about, because I

00:12:32.880 --> 00:12:35.350
said, 'Lord, tonight,

00:12:35.360 --> 00:12:38.310
I'm disappointed inside.'Not 'boy,'but inside of

00:12:38.310 --> 00:12:38.320
me,

00:12:38.320 --> 00:12:40.870
I'm

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:42.550
disappointed inside for how I've seen

00:12:42.560 --> 00:12:45.509
crypto beaten this last week. And I was

